        <div id="body" class="">
            
            
            

<p>With <b>MathTran</b> you can to create, store and translate
mathematical content.</p>

 
</p>

<p>Using the formula editor, you can interactively
<b>create</b> mathematical formulas.</p>

<p>If you have an account, you can <b>store</b> the
formulas you create.</p>

<p>MathTran <b>translates</b> TeX-notation mathematics to images (for
inclusion in web pages and on emails) as a web service.</p>

<p>If you have any question, please <a
href="mailto:support@mathtran.org">email us</a>.</p>


 
<p>Would you like to <a href="/account/signup/">sign up</a> for an account?  It only takes a minute or two.  Or you can start by browsing the
<a href="/formulas/ ">latest formulas</a>.
</p>
 



            
